        <para id="id8140926">When Susan and Paul looked at the map, they decided to go and help Lisa.</para>
        <list id="id7242527" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Discuss how they will travel and what they will need to take with them. Make a list of everything they will need.</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id1128545">
          <media id="id1128545_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics4-98c5.png" id="id1128545__onlineimage" height="313" width="576"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <list id="id8491977" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>You have made a good list if you remember all these things. If you think of something else of importance you must write down why Paul and Susan will need it.</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id8535168">
          <media id="id8535168_media" alt="">
