        <list id="id1168890778058" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>When you have finished, look at your list. Do you think your ideas are good? Put a blue tick under the face that shows how you feel about your ideas. </item>
          <item>Discuss your lists with the rest of the class. Now look at your own list. Put a red dot to show what you feel about your list now.</item>
        </list>
