        <para id="id6508174">Paul and Susan could not wait to ask their parents if they could go and help Lisa. They decided to leave a note telling them where they had gone so that they would not be worried.</para>
        <para id="id7235117">What should they say? Pretend that you are Paul or Susan. Write a note to your Mom telling her where you are going. </para>
